com.github.douglasorr.shared

Interface SharedList<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<T>, Iterable<T>, List<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinkedList

    public interface SharedList<T>
extends List<T>
    A list that supports shared updates in place of mutable ones. Apart from this, it behaves as a normal Java immutable List.

    Instead of using LinkedList.addFirst, use prepend(Object), and instead of using LinkedList.removeFirst, use tail(). The accessor head() is provided for convenience.
